			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Name-That-Shifter-42.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-65818" title="Name That Shifter 42" src="http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Name-That-Shifter-42.jpg" alt="" width="626" height="110" /></a></p>
<div id="attachment_65819" class="wp-caption alignright" style="width: 160px"><a href="http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Shifter-No.-42.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-65819" title="Shifter No. 42" src="http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Shifter-No.-42-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Click to enlarge</p></div>
<p>On Monday we presented this week’s shifter and asked you to identify the make and model of the vehicle from whence it came. Several of you recognized the shifter as a 1980s-era Chrysler unit. The first commenter to correctly identify it as a 1985 Chrysler Laser XE was J D., who will receive a <a href="http://shop.caranddriver.com/store/hfmedia/en_US/DisplayCategoryProductListPage/categoryID.49796200/parentCategoryID.19556100">Save the Manuals</a> button and sticker as a reward.</p>
<p>The Laser pictured here is from our May 1985 issue, where it placed seventh in an eight-car comparison test. It was powered by a turbocharged 2.2-liter four-cylinder making 146 hp, which endowed it with a quick (among its competitive set) 8.1-second 0-to-60 time. Of the eight “sporty” coupes, the quickest to 60 was the Ford Mustang SVO, at 6.8 seconds. The slowest? The Chevrolet Camaro Berlinetta, which took 10 seconds to reach the same speed.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/1985-Chrysler-Laser-XE.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-66014" title="1985 Chrysler Laser XE" src="http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/1985-Chrysler-Laser-XE-626x382.jpg" alt="" width="626" height="382" /></a><a href="http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/1985-Chrysler-Laser-XE-interior.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-66015" title="1985 Chrysler Laser XE interior" src="http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/1985-Chrysler-Laser-XE-interior-626x382.jpg" alt="" width="626" height="382" /></a></p>
<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~4/OpOBactdWwQ" height="1" width="1"/>]]></content:encoded>
